title: UFYB 262: What Blocks Us from New Beliefs: A Conversation with Brooke Castillo Part 2
itunes:title: What Blocks Us from New Beliefs: A Conversation with Brooke Castillo Part 2
description:
Giving yourself permission to want the things you want *and* to go out and get them is one of the most powerful decisions you can make in your life – and it’s also one of the hardest. This week I continue my conversation with my friend and mentor Brooke Castillo where we dive into the feeling of worthiness, why it’s ok to want more than what you have, and how tapping into what you really want helps you show up most powerfully in the world.

 

Get full show notes and more information here: https://unfuckyourbrain.com/262
